CHANGELOG

0.1.1.0
	- FEATURE: Added ability to clear/open logs within the plugin window
	- FEATURE: Added startup command/message to announcements tab, leave blank for none. (announcements now only go out after inital delay)
	- FEATURE: Added ability to disable all announcements from announcements tab.
	- FEATURE: Added /dtb forcebuff command
	- FEATURE: Added option keep tinkering equipment equipped for x seconds after tink job, so consecutive tinks are faster (default 30s).
	- FEATURE: Added option in main config tab to respond to unknown commands
	- FIX: Fixed issue where items added to equipment lists that disappeared caused the list to break.
	- FIX: Don't send duplicate messages within time window (config file only currently, DontResendDuplicateMessagesWindow, default 2s).
	- FIX: Fixed bug where equipment spells could cause infinite buffing loop
	- FIX: Force add -b- to all bot chat/emote spam
	- FIX: Added seconds to timestamp in debuglog.txt
	- FIX: Speed up item equip/dequip cycle
	- Tested on 1.25 (need rare/foolproof support)

